🌦️ Weather App
A modern weather application that provides real-time weather updates, forecasts, and location-based weather information with a clean and responsive user interface.
✨ Features
🌍 Search weather by city name
📍 Current location weather support
🌡️ Real-time temperature display
💧 Humidity information
💨 Wind speed details
☁️ Weather conditions and icons
📅 Multi-day weather forecast
🌙 Responsive and user-friendly design
⚡ Fast and lightweight
🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript / React
Weather API: OpenWeatherMap API
Hosting: Vercel / Netlify
